quran[9{c,v,t}:
27,14,unhon ne sara sar zulm aur ghuroor ki raah se un nishanion ka inkaar kya halaank dil un ke qaail ho chuke thay ab dekh lau ke un mfsdon ka injaam kaisa howa
27,15,( doosri taraf ) hum ne DAWOD o sulaiman ko ilm ataa kya aur unhon ne kaha ke shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hum ko apne bohat se momin bundon par fazeelat ataa ki
27,16,"aur DAWOD ka waris sulaiman howa aur is ne kaha"" “logo, hamein parindon ki buliyan sikhayi gayi hain aur hamein har terhan ki cheeze di gayi hain, bay shak yeh ( Allah ka ) numaya fazl hai """
27,17,sulaiman ke liye jin aur insanon aur parindon ke lashkar jama kiye gay thay aur woh poooray zabt mein rakhay jatay thay
27,18,"( aik martaba woh un ke sath coach kar raha tha ) yahan taq ke jab yeh sab chyontyon ki waadi mein puhanche to aik choonti ne kaha"" “ay chuntiyo, apne bilon mein ghis jao, kahin aisa nah ho ke sulaiman aur is ke lashkar tumhe kuchal dalain aur inhen khabar bhi nah ho """
27,19,"sulaiman is ki baat par Muskuratay hue hans para aur bola"" ae mere rab, mujhe qaboo mein rakh ke mein tairay is ahsaan ka shukar ada karta rahon jo to ne mujh par aur mere walidain par kya hai aur aisa amal Saleh karoon jo tujhe pasand aeye aur apni rehmat se mujh ko apne Saleh bundon mein daakhil kar """
27,20,( aik aur mauqa par ) sulaiman ne parindon ka jaiza liya aur kaha “کیا baat hai ke mein falan hُd hُd ko nahi dekh raha hon kya woh kahin gayab ho gaya hai ?
27,21,"mein usay sakht saza dun ga, ya zibah kar dun ga, warna usay mere samnay maqool wajah paish karni ho gi"
27,22,"kuch ziyada der nah guzri thi ke uss ne aa kar kaha"" “min ne woh maloomat haasil ki hain jo aap ke ilm mein nahi hain mein saba ke mutaliq yakeeni ittila le kar aaya hon"
